*** ## üìù Table of Contents - [Highlights](#highlights) - [Installation](#installation) - [Built Using](#built_using) - [Documentation](#documentation) ## ‚ú® Highlights This package offers a set of tools to make your testing easier and boost your development workflow. * Easy to use * Lightweight * Tested What's inside: * Mocking: Create mocks for modules and functions without the hassle. * Auto-Mocking: Automatically generate mocks for complex objects to keep your tests clean and * Custom Timers: Simulate time in your tests with a fake timer that supports setTimeout and setInterval. * Global DOM Control: Manage global DOM settings effortlessly for your web app tests (using [@happy-dom/global-registrator](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@happy-dom/global-registrator)). ## üîå Installation

```bash
# NPM
npm install --save-dev @itsmeid/bun-test-utils

# BUN
bun add -d @itsmeid/bun-test-utils
```
